WHEELER, Respondent, v. WATERTOWN ST. RY. CO., Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by Jane E. Wheeler, as administratrix, etc., against the Watertown Street Railway Company.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment and order affirmed, with costs.
